Here are 30 reusable JSON prompt templates covering many common AI tasks. You can adapt them for ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, local LLMs, or agent frameworks.

# 1. Text Summarization

```json
{
  "task": "summarize",
  "input": "<text>",
  "output": {
    "summary": "",
    "key_points": [],
    "action_items": []
  }
}
```

